CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 3, 1959, pg. A14 reads: "Merrymakers - Having fun between dance sets at the swank Pittsburghers Club formal last Friday at the Hotel Roosevelt was the above group. Left to right: Mr. and Mrs. Clifford Morrison, Mr. and Mrs. Milfred (Pete) Jackson, Mrs. Berneta Young of Mansfield, Ohio; Joseph Coy, Mr. and Mrs. Robert Jordan of Harrisburg - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Pittsburghers Club members and guests, from left: Mr. and Mrs. Clifford Morrison, Mr. and Mrs. Milfred (Pete) Jackson, Berneta Young, Joseph Coy, and Mr. and Mrs. Robert Jordan, standing in Roosevelt Hotel for Bicentennial dance
